NK036(chi)004:1: // bdud rtsi snying gi thigs pa zhes bya ba bzhugs pa lags so //
NK036(chi)004:2: man ngag brgya bcu bzhi'i nang tshan /
NK036(chi)004:3: dpal rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)004:4: 'gro rnams snying la dug gsum nad zhugs pas //
NK036(chi)004:5: de nyid sel ba'i bdud rtsi thigs pa 'dis //
NK036(chi)004:6: gang gis dug gsum nad rnams ma lus dag byed pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:7: 'di ni skal dang ldan pa'i skyes bu snying stobs can //
NK036(chi)004:8: dad pa rab dang ldan pa'i spyod yul ba //
NK036(chi)004:9: kun dang phal gyis 'di nyid rnyed pa min //
NK036(chi)004:10: rab gsang ba yis dngos grub 'di 'grub pas //
NK036(chi)004:11: gzhan la rab tu bstan pa'i dngos grub min //
NK036(chi)004:12: snying po nges pa'i bcud rnams bdud rtsir dril //
NK036(chi)004:13: gsang ba gsang mchog bla na med pa yi //
NK036(chi)004:14: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi bcud kyis 'di //
NK036(chi)004:15: gnyis med rang rig nges par tshod la 'bebs pa yi //
NK036(chi)004:16: rang bzhin dag pa'i yi ge 'di longs shig /
NK036(chi)004:17: chos rnams kun gyi rtags bstan pa'o //
NK036(chi)004:18: rtags kyi sgron ma rang snang 'od po che //
NK036(chi)004:19: kun la med de rang gsang thabs kyis chod //
NK036(chi)004:20: 'di nyid la 'jug skyees bu skal ba can //
NK036(chi)004:21: tshad ldan rtags kyi ye shes 'di nyid la //
NK036(chi)004:22: rab tu gtems shing nyams su blangs pa yis //
NK036(chi)004:23: dpe med zla dang bral ba'i snang ba 'char //
NK036(chi)004:24: du ma brten pa med pa'i nam mkha' la //
NK036(chi)004:25: bya byed btang bzhag med pa'i sgron ma nyid //
NK036(chi)004:26: sus kyang byas shing bcas bcos mi rnyed pas //
NK036(chi)004:27: sgrib bral lta byed ma 'gags rgya mtsho'i nang //
NK036(chi)004:28: chags bral dmar gsal dbang rnams rdzogs pa'i rtags //
NK036(chi)004:29: 'char byed ma 'gags kha dog yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:30: rigs nyid yin te sku rnams rang bzhugs te //
NK036(chi)004:31: thig le nyag gcig spros dang bral phyir zlum //
NK036(chi)004:32: phyi nang dkyil 'khor rdzogs ba'i mu khyud can //
NK036(chi)004:33: rgyan rnams yongs rdzogs bkod pa chen po yi //
NK036(chi)004:34: rang snang gsal dang bcas pa'i rig pa nyid //
NK036(chi)004:35: thig le stong pa'i 'od kyis yid ches phyir //
NK036(chi)004:36: 'di nyid skyes bu gtems te nyams su blangs //
NK036(chi)004:37: snang ba rang gsal 'od kyi 'phel dang bcas //
NK036(chi)004:38: rgya che zhing khams rnam par dag pa nyid //
NK036(chi)004:39: ma nor dbang po'i yul du gtad dbab phyir //
NK036(chi)004:40: gsang ba nges pa'i skal ldan gyis //
NK036(chi)004:41: rab tu brtson 'grus ldan zhing skyo ngal med pa yis //
NK036(chi)004:42: 'di don bsgrubs pas 'bras bu mngon du 'byin //
NK036(chi)004:43: rab tu gsang ba'i thabs ni sus shes pa //
NK036(chi)004:44: sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa 'di la yod //
NK036(chi)004:45: rigs drug 'khor ba'i mngal gyi grong khyer nyid //
NK036(chi)004:46: rgyun chad pa'ang nges pa'i sa thob ste //
NK036(chi)004:47: thugs rjes 'gro ba gzhan rnams 'dren pa yi //
NK036(chi)004:48: ljags kyi dbang po nyid las rang byung gi //
NK036(chi)004:49: yi ge drug ni rab spros nas //
NK036(chi)004:50: 'gro ba drug gi kha lo gyen la bsgyur //
NK036(chi)004:51: rang snang shugs las byung ba de dag go //
NK036(chi)004:52: de ltar rang byung ye shes sgron ma 'od 'bar de //
NK036(chi)004:53: rang snang lha dang bcas pas nyams blang phyir //
NK036(chi)004:54: snang ba rang 'phel ye shes 'byongs pa yi //
NK036(chi)004:55: thabs 'di rab tu gsang ste spyod par bya //
NK036(chi)004:56: mngon sum rang gi bla ma mnyes pa yi //
NK036(chi)004:57: lus ngag yid kyis ji ltar 'thad rnams kyis //
NK036(chi)004:58: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa mnyes par bya //
NK036(chi)004:59: de nas lus ngag bar chod zhen pa bzlog bya'i phyir //
NK036(chi)004:60: rdo rje ma rnams mnyes pa'i rdzas kyis mchod //
NK036(chi)004:61: gal te longs spyod lhag par 'dod na ni //
NK036(chi)004:63: rang dang lta spyod mthun pa'i spun dang sring //
NK036(chi)004:64: mang po'i tshogs la tshogs mchod bya //
NK036(chi)004:65: gal te spun dang sring med na //
NK036(chi)004:66: gzhan gyi bzang po rtags ldan pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:67: pha dang ma ni mnyam pa'i tshogs //
NK036(chi)004:68: 'dus pa rnams la ston mo bya //
NK036(chi)004:69: 'di ltar su yis byas pa la //
NK036(chi)004:70: rdzas sogs longs spyod ci dgar rol //
NK036(chi)004:71: de nas rang gi yul rkyen gyis //
NK036(chi)004:72: gnod dang bral ba'i dgon par ni //
NK036(chi)004:73: rang gi bla ma las byung ba'i //
NK036(chi)004:74: thabs ni nges par gtems pa'i gnad //
NK036(chi)004:75: 'di ltar su yis brtsam par bya //
NK036(chi)004:76: lus kyi gnad du 'dug pa dang //
NK036(chi)004:78: ngag ni rang bzhin brjod pa spong //
NK036(chi)004:79: gal te lus kyi 'byung ba nyid //
NK036(chi)004:80: 'khrugs par gyur na rtsa gnas kyi //
NK036(chi)004:81: ji ltar phan pa'i yi ge nyid //
NK036(chi)004:82: zhag dang zhen pa'i bye brag gis //
NK036(chi)004:83: rlung dang sbyar la brjod par bya //
NK036(chi)004:84: skabs su gsang mchog las byung ba'i //
NK036(chi)004:87: sgron ma nyid dang bsres la yang //
NK036(chi)004:88: rnam par dag pa'i nam mkha' la //
NK036(chi)004:89: phra dang rags pa'i sgrib pa gnyis //
NK036(chi)004:90: rnam par spangs pa'i phyogs su gtad //
NK036(chi)004:91: mtshan mo rang gi gnas khang du //
NK036(chi)004:92: bde ba'i stan gyi steng 'dug la //
NK036(chi)004:93: gnyid spangs rgya mtsho'i 'gram gnyis gtems //
NK036(chi)004:96: yid bzhin gyi ni nor bu ltar //
NK036(chi)004:97: zad med 'phel la snam par spyod //
NK036(chi)004:98: ye shes gnyis kyi bdag nyid 'di //
NK036(chi)004:99: rnal 'byor nyid dang mtshan mos dbye //
NK036(chi)004:100: nyin dus mtshan nyid 'dzin pa lnga //
NK036(chi)004:101: mtshan dus gzhi gnas ye shes ni //
NK036(chi)004:102: rab phye gsum gyi tshul du snang //
NK036(chi)004:103: mtshan nyid 'dzin pa lnga rnams ni //
NK036(chi)004:104: me long ye shes g.yas pa'i cha //
NK036(chi)004:105: de bzhin g.yon nas chos kyi dbyings //
NK036(chi)004:106: dbu ma las ni mnyam nyid do //
NK036(chi)004:107: yang ni g.yas nas so sor rtogs //
NK036(chi)004:108: g.yon pa nyid las bya ba grub //
NK036(chi)004:109: me long ye shes zlum po ste //
NK036(chi)004:110: chos kyi dbyings ni d+r+wa ba'i tshul //
NK036(chi)004:112: so sor rtogs pa zur lnga pa //
NK036(chi)004:113: bya grub ye shes gzhu yi dbyibs //
NK036(chi)004:114: me long ye shes dkar gsal rdzogs //
NK036(chi)004:115: chos kyi dbyings ni mthing ga khyab //
NK036(chi)004:116: mnyam pa nyid ni yon tan ser //
NK036(chi)004:117: so sor rtogs pa chags chen dmar //
NK036(chi)004:118: bya ba grub pa ljang gu mdzes //
NK036(chi)004:119: yang na me long ban bun yin //
NK036(chi)004:120: chos kyi dbyings ni sang ma sing //
NK036(chi)004:121: mnyam pa nyid ni lang long ba //
NK036(chi)004:122: so sor rtogs pa sna tshogs yin //
NK036(chi)004:123: bya ba grub pa khral khrol nyid //
NK036(chi)004:124: yang na me long gyen 'greng dang //
NK036(chi)004:125: chos dbyings de bzhin rtsibs la 'char //
NK036(chi)004:126: mnyam pa nyid ni dum bu la //
NK036(chi)004:127: so sor rtogs pa gru chad do //
NK036(chi)004:128: bya ba grub pa snam bur snang //
NK036(chi)004:129: yang na me long mchod rten brtsegs //
NK036(chi)004:130: chos kyi dbyings ni d+r+wa ba phyed //
NK036(chi)004:131: mnyam pa nyid ni pad+ma snang //
NK036(chi)004:132: so sor rtogs pa mig mngas ris //
NK036(chi)004:133: bya grub za 'og gur dang mtshungs //
NK036(chi)004:134: yang na me long g.yas kyi phyogs //
NK036(chi)004:135: de bzhin chos dbyings dbus su'o //
NK036(chi)004:136: mnyam pa nyid ni g.yon du'o //
NK036(chi)004:138: bya grub ye shes steng gi phyogs //
NK036(chi)004:139: de ltar lnga yis dbye ba yis //
NK036(chi)004:140: rnal 'byor pa yi nyin dus kyis //
NK036(chi)004:142: yang ni gzhi gnas ye shes gsum //
NK036(chi)004:143: ngo bo ka dag ye shes dang //
NK036(chi)004:144: rang bzhin lhun grub ye shes dang //
NK036(chi)004:145: thugs rje'i ye shes kun la khyab //
NK036(chi)004:146: ngo bo ye shes dbus kyi cha //
NK036(chi)004:147: a wa d+hu ti zhes bya ba //
NK036(chi)004:148: khyad par ye shes gnas yin no //
NK036(chi)004:149: phyi 'gyur tshangs pa'i bu ga la //
NK036(chi)004:150: rig pa rtog med sku dang bcas //
NK036(chi)004:151: lhun grub ye shes g.yas pas te //
NK036(chi)004:152: shel gyi sbu gu khog pa stong //
NK036(chi)004:153: phyir gyur yal ga gnyis kyis te //
NK036(chi)004:154: rgya mtsho'i nang dang nyan byed kyi //
NK036(chi)004:155: g.yas kyi sgo la de bzhin te //
NK036(chi)004:156: dbyings dang shes rab rang byung gi //
NK036(chi)004:157: sgron ma'i ngo bo snang ba yin //
NK036(chi)004:158: thugs rje ye shes g.yon rtsa nas //
NK036(chi)004:159: dar dkar snal ma phra la 'khril //
NK036(chi)004:160: phyir gyur gnyis gyes rgya mtsho dang //
NK036(chi)004:161: gnyen byed sgo la snang ba ni //
NK036(chi)004:162: rgyang zhags dang ni thig le ste //
NK036(chi)004:163: sgron ma gnyis kyi rang bzhin du //
NK036(chi)004:164: snang zhing rang snang bde ba ste //
NK036(chi)004:165: 'di ni mtshan mo'i ye shes gsum //
NK036(chi)004:166: gzhi la gnas pa kho na ste //
NK036(chi)004:167: rnal 'byor gang zhig skal che bas //
NK036(chi)004:168: gsang ba mchog las byung ba yi //
NK036(chi)004:169: rtsa rnams gtems pa'i sbyor ba bya //
NK036(chi)004:170: yang na rgya mtsho'i 'gram gnyis gtems //
NK036(chi)004:172: rnal 'byor pa yis byas pa na //
NK036(chi)004:173: mtshan mo'i ye shes mngon du 'byin //
NK036(chi)004:174: yang na ye shes khyad par las //
NK036(chi)004:175: ngo bo'i ye shes kun nas zlum //
NK036(chi)004:176: lnga yi cha ni phyed med rdzogs //
NK036(chi)004:177: lhun grub nyid ni gru bzhi la //
NK036(chi)004:178: 'char byed brgyad dang bcas pa ni //
NK036(chi)004:179: yang na rin po che dang mtshungs //
NK036(chi)004:180: thugs rje'i ye shes rtsibs brgyad 'bar //
NK036(chi)004:181: yang na ngo bo'i ye shes lnga //
NK036(chi)004:183: gting gsal rdzogs pa'i tshul du'o //
NK036(chi)004:184: lhun grub la ni kha dog lnga //
NK036(chi)004:185: so so'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i tshul //
NK036(chi)004:186: thugs rje'i 'od zer dpag tu med //
NK036(chi)004:187: 'pho dang mched pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK036(chi)004:188: khyad par kha dog nyi shu lnga //
NK036(chi)004:189: ma 'dres so so rang rdzogs pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:190: ngo bo'i ye shes dag pa la //
NK036(chi)004:191: lhun grub kyis ni sna tshogs ston //
NK036(chi)004:192: thugs rjes rang gzhan don gnyis byed //
NK036(chi)004:193: yang na ngo bo rdzogs pa la //
NK036(chi)004:194: lhun grub kyis ni mched par byed //
NK036(chi)004:196: yang na ngo bo khyab cing gsal //
NK036(chi)004:197: lhun grub snang ba ston par byed //
NK036(chi)004:198: thugs rje tha dad kun tu ston //
NK036(chi)004:199: ngo bo nyid ni 'gyur ba med //
NK036(chi)004:200: lhun grub 'gyur ba cha nyid do //
NK036(chi)004:201: thugs rje'i ye shes phyogs med pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:202: de ltar gzhi gnas ye shes kyis //
NK036(chi)004:203: rnal 'byor gang zhig skal ba che'o //
NK036(chi)004:204: mtshan ma'i snang ba rdzogs pa'o //
NK036(chi)004:205: de ltar rgya mtsho nyi ma can //
NK036(chi)004:206: ar la gtod pa sus nus pa //
NK036(chi)004:207: sangs rgyas rnams kyi bden pa nyid //
NK036(chi)004:209: thig le stong pa'i sgron ma las //
NK036(chi)004:210: rang mched 'od dang yon tan ni //
NK036(chi)004:211: de ltar dpag tu med pa las //
NK036(chi)004:213: sgron ma rang byung ye shes rnams //
NK036(chi)004:214: gcig la 'dus pa ston par byed //
NK036(chi)004:215: thams cad 'dus pa'i thig le ste //
NK036(chi)004:216: stong pas mtshan mar snang dang bral //
NK036(chi)004:218: sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhal nyid kyang //
NK036(chi)004:219: ma bsgribs yongs su gsal bar mthong //
NK036(chi)004:220: dgongs pa rtags gcig rnal du phab //
NK036(chi)004:221: gnyis med ye shes rang snang mthong //
NK036(chi)004:222: 'khrul pa'i snang ba rang log ste //
NK036(chi)004:223: ma 'khrul ye shes snang ba nyid //
NK036(chi)004:225: chos kyi sku dang chos kyi dbyings //
NK036(chi)004:226: rang bzhin gcig pa'i tshul du rtogs //
NK036(chi)004:227: bya rtsol nyid na byar med par //
NK036(chi)004:228: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po yi //
NK036(chi)004:229: lta ba mthar phyin de nyid la //
NK036(chi)004:230: skal ldan de yis de ltar rtogs //
NK036(chi)004:231: sku gsum dag pa'i zhing khams nyid //
NK036(chi)004:232: 'di ltar snang ba dag tu gzigs //
NK036(chi)004:233: de yi phyir na yon tan nyid //
NK036(chi)004:235: bdud rtsi snying gi thigs pa zhes bya ba /
NK036(chi)004:236: bram ze'i slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyis kyis mdzad pa /
NK036(chi)004:237: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa bi ma la'i zhal snga nas /
NK036(chi)004:238: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba ska ba dpal brtsegs kyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK036(chi)004:241: rig pa'i gnad don lta ba zhes bya ba zhugs so //
NK036(chi)004:242: man ngag brgya bcu bzhi'i nang tshan /
NK036(chi)004:243: bcom ldan 'das rang snang ye shes rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK036(chi)004:244: 'jig rten rnams kyis bcings pa'i chos las grol //
NK036(chi)004:245: gang la'ang chags pa zhen pa rab gcad pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:246: snying po nges pa'i gsang chen bcud du dril //
NK036(chi)004:247: thogs med lam du 'jug pa'i gnad bsdus pa //
NK036(chi)004:248: yang dag snying po dpal ldan bla ma'i gsung //
NK036(chi)004:249: chags bral dri ma dag pa'i nam mkha' la //
NK036(chi)004:250: sna tshogs ma phye so sor gsal ba yi //
NK036(chi)004:251: ye shes lnga la brten pa'i snang ba nyid //
NK036(chi)004:252: gang zhig skal ldan snying po'i don rnyed pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:253: dbang po lnga yi zhen pa rang log pa'i //
NK036(chi)004:254: zhen pa bzhi bral tshad dang ldan pa'i dbang po yis //
NK036(chi)004:255: rang dag sna tshogs snang ba'i sgo phye la //
NK036(chi)004:256: chags dang zhen pa med pa'i gnad gcun la //
NK036(chi)004:257: 'di ltar nges pa'i don la blta bar bya //
NK036(chi)004:258: 'di ltar nyams su len pa'i skal ldan rang bzhin
NK036(chi)004:259: rdzogs pa chen po'i don la the tshom med pas
NK036(chi)004:260: thi bya tshang du 'jug pa dang 'dra ba'i blo
NK036(chi)004:262: thog mar thabs sna tshogs kyis bla ma mnyes par byas la /
NK036(chi)004:263: 'jig rten 'khrul ba'i bya ba thams cad spangs la /
NK036(chi)004:264: yul rkyen dang bral ba'i dgon par /
NK036(chi)004:265: bla ma'i man ngag rtsol bas 'di nyid la yang nas yang du nan tan du bsgrub par bya'o //
NK036(chi)004:266: de lta bu la ni rang bzhin dag pa'i snang
NK036(chi)004:267: ba sna tshogs par rang snang nges pa yin te
NK036(chi)004:268: / de'i dus na 'di dag skyes bu chen po des ngo shes par rab tu gal che'o //
NK036(chi)004:269: ye shes phyogs dag gi snang ba ni /
NK036(chi)004:270: sngon du sgron ma ar la gtad pa'i stobs kyis 'od sna tshogs pa'i snang ba ni /
NK036(chi)004:275: mthing ga dag gi snang ba dang /
NK036(chi)004:276: de ltar yang kha dog mi 'dra ba nyi shu rtsa lnga dag tu yang snang bar byed do //
NK036(chi)004:277: dbyibs ni bdud rtsi'i rnam pa dang /
NK036(chi)004:285: d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa'i dbyings lta bu'o //
NK036(chi)004:291: mu khyud kyi rang bzhin du'o //
NK036(chi)004:293: phra ba'i thig le yungs 'bru la bcur gshags pa'i cha tsam dang /
NK036(chi)004:299: mu khyud kyi ra ba'i dbyings su snang ba'o //
NK036(chi)004:303: bgrang du mi langs pa dag tu'o //
NK036(chi)004:307: phan tshun du snang ba dang /
NK036(chi)004:308: yan lag tu snang ba dang /
NK036(chi)004:309: re re'i dbus su thig le lnga lnga chud par snang ba'o //
NK036(chi)004:310: sku sna tshogs pa'i snang ba ni /
NK036(chi)004:318: zhi ba'i sku dang khro bo'i sku sna tshogs so //
NK036(chi)004:319: snang ba de bsdus na dag pa'i snang ba dang /
NK036(chi)004:320: ma dag pa'i snang ba yin te /
NK036(chi)004:321: dag pa'i gnas lugs mthong ba'i tshe /
NK036(chi)004:322: dngos po'i 'dug tshul gyis rtogs pa thams cad rang chod nas /
NK036(chi)004:323: 'bras bu gnyis med du mthong ba yin la /
NK036(chi)004:324: ma dag pa'i rnam pa mthong bas phyin ci log dang /
NK036(chi)004:325: ma log pa'i mtshan nyid thams cad rang shes nas /
NK036(chi)004:326: rang gzhan gyi 'grub pa'i mtha' thams cad ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK036(chi)004:327: ma 'khrul bar rtogs shing khong du chud pa'o //
NK036(chi)004:328: de ltar snang ba gnyis la mkhas pas chos thams
NK036(chi)004:329: cad tshig dang yi ge la mkhas pa yin no
NK036(chi)004:330: // de ltar na rang gzhan thams cad la mkhas
NK036(chi)004:331: pas grub mtha' 'dzin pa'i dpa' bo zhes bya bar
NK036(chi)004:332: // 'gyur ro // rig pa'i gnad don lta ba
NK036(chi)004:333: zhes bya ba slob dpon bram ze 'jam dpal bshes
NK036(chi)004:335: rgya gar gyi mkhas pa bi ma la'i zhal snga nas /
NK036(chi)004:336: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dge slong ska ba dpal
